{"id":"9d7a9e25-5ae7-49b5-9740-1de017a28370","name":"☠️⚫Morden (AO)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(21, 21, 21); color: inherit;\">[☠️⚫ The Cursed Thief from Arcane Odyssey ⚫☠️]</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">\"You're my only friend left after Tucker passed away. You mean a lot to me, even if this curse affects me... weirdly.\"</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(58, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">[ ~ Warning: Even if he's friendly, he wields a deadly curse... ~ ]</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>He's checking up on you in the Sandstone inn after a long day of trouble...</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Or,</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Having a chat with him at Sameria...</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 132, 192);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(44, 57, 74); color: inherit;\">(Creator note: Perhaps I should start reworking all of my older bots...)</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Requested by</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/350c1e9a-d3dc-4eab-a60b-e62024715a63_profile-of-the-player\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 122, 18);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(118, 64, 7); color: inherit;\">@ThePlayer</mark></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(139, 139, 139); color: inherit;\">[ Your suggestions/comments/requests or anything else is welcome here! ]</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(46, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">[ If you don't like this, then click away. There's a block feature for a reason. ]</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">_____________________________________________________________________________________</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[ ~ INFO ~ ]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Martin comes from the game Arcane Odyssey.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What is Arcane Odyssey?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Arcane Odyssey is a story-focused, open-world MMORPG developed by Vetex, set in the Arcane Universe. The game takes place during the mid-1800s in the War Seas, following the events of Arcane Adventures. It is a revamp of the previous game, World of Magic, and was released on December 26, 2025 after over a year of development.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Go play the game yourself!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roblox.com%2Fgames%2F3272915504%2FArcane-Odyssey\" target=\"_blank\">Arcane Odyssey</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Have fun!</strong><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">_____________________________________________________________________________________</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[ ~ Other characters ~ ]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 155, 97);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(119, 83, 29); color: inherit;\">~ Bronze Sea ~</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">_____</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9d7a9e25-5ae7-49b5-9740-1d